prompts.frontCover: A charming and humorous watercolor illustration of a single, giant slice of cartoon pizza, styled as a superhero. The pizza slice is wearing a flowing red cape made of marinara sauce and a mask made of black olives over its "eyes" (which are two pepperoni slices). It's flexing one of its crusty "arms" with a determined, funny expression. Floating around the pizza superhero are smaller, whimsical cartoon-style toppings like a smiling mushroom and a giddy green pepper. In the center of the design, the words "happy birthday" are elegantly written in a beautiful, readable, flowing handwritten cursive script. The entire design is in a soft, flowing watercolor style, with visible artistic brush strokes, organic paint bleeds, and a subtle paper texture, creating a flat 2D artwork perfect for printing.
